      "content": "Wait, you're telling me you aren't actually low on stock? That's fine, but my manager is breathing down my neck about these numbers. If you aren't ready to commit to this price right now, I have to move to the next buyer on my list. I can't sit here and wait around for an \"intelligence agent\" who isn't sure about their requirements. If you want this deal, tell me right now: is this an emergency order for your production line or am I wasting my time?",
